These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Movie-Genre: documentary, horror, satire, comedy
Nationality: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. Nationality:egyptian is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1
2. Movie-Genre:documentary == Nationality:turkish##1
3. Nationality:thai is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1
4. Movie-Genre:horror is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1
5. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | comedy | satire | horror | documentary   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
Music-Genre: house, metal, blues, classical
1. Hobby:woodworking == Music-Genre:metal##1
2. Hobby:camping is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:cooking is on the right of Hobby:woodworking##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the right of Music-Genre:blues##1
5. Music-Genre:metal is on the left of Music-Genre:house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | metal      | house | classical |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Hobby: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
Game: domino, chess, billiard, backgammon
1. Game:billiard is on the left of Game:backgammon##1
2. Hobby:fishing == Game:domino##1
3. Game:chess is on the far right##1
4. Game:backgammon is on the right of Hobby:writing##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Game:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Game   | domino   | billiard | backgammon | chess         |

