3. Color:white is on the left of Color:green##1
4. Color:white is on the right of Color:black##1
5. Sport:basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | black | white | green  | pink      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

