2. Beverage:almond-milk is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:american is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1
4. Nationality:nigerian == Beverage:milk##1
5. Beverage:7up is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Beverage     | soy-milk  | 7up    | almond-milk       | milk |

 